                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg flex items-center gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-plane text-red-600"></i> Flight Departure — British Airways BA031</h3>
                        <div class="mt-3 text-sm space-y-2">
                            <div><strong>Target at LHR T5:</strong> 16:20 (3 hours before 19:20 departure)</div>
                            <div><strong>From central London:</strong> Heathrow Express from Paddington (~21 mins) or Elizabeth line / Tube.</div>
                            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">Book Heathrow Express tickets in advance for best price.</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <a href="https://www.heathrowexpress.com/" target="_blank" class="inline-block bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-2xl text-sm font-semibold">Heathrow Express Tickets</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
