            <div class="money-tip mt-6 p-5 rounded-3xl">
                <div class="font-semibold text-amber-900">Departure Day Savings</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-amber-800">• Use contactless payment or Oyster card for all London transport.<br>• Heathrow Express is fastest but book ahead; Elizabeth line is cheaper and still quick.<br>• Light lunch at The Orangery or bring picnic to the park to keep costs down before the flight.</div>
